title: Jules Thin Crust Pizza
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Counter service style pizza restaurant that serves thin crust pizza and organic salads. Flour and tomato sauce are organic. Tries to use local and organic ingredients when possible. Gluten-free crust (contains eggs) and whole wheat crust (contains honey). All dressings contain honey or worcestershire sauce. At least 15 veg toppings combinations, 2 dairy-free. Stocks vegan cheese.
